s)\n  - P6: Dual-carbonyl convergence route (9 steps)\n  - P7: Formate-centered redundant route (12 steps)\n  - P8: Aminoacetonitrile-reservoir route (8 steps)\n  - P9: Glycolaldehyde-supported carbonyl diversification route (8 steps)\n  - P10: Full cross-environment integrated route (13 steps)\n\nHUB MOLECULES: mol_004, mol_005, mol_007, mol_008, mol_011\nCONVERGENCE POINTS: 4\n\n\nPlease evaluate the network and respond with JSON:\n{\n    \"pathway_evaluations\": [\n        {\n            \"pathway_id\": \"<id>\",\n            \"reaction_scores\": {\"rxn_001\": 0.85, ...},\n            \"chemical_feasibility\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"pathway_coherence\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"environmental_progression\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"target_achievement\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"overall_confidence\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"feedback\": \"<pathway-specific feedback>\",\n            \"approved\": <true if confidence >= 0.8>,\n            \"problematic_reactions\": [\"rxn_ids with issues\"],\n            \"suggestions\": [\"improvements\"]\n        }\n    ],\n    \"best_pathway_id\": \"<id of best pathway>\",\n    \"overall_confidence\": <0.0-1.0>,\n    \"network_feedback\": \"<overall assessment>\",\n    \"approved\": <true if any pathway approved>,\n    \"hub_quality\": <0.0-1.0>,\n    \"convergence_quality\": <0.0-1.0>\n}\n", "raw_response": "{\n  \"pathway_evaluations\": [\n    {\n      \"pathway_id\": \"P1\",\n      \"reaction_scores\": {\n        \"rxn_001\": 0.92,\n        \"rxn_002\": 0.84,\n        \"rxn_003\": 0.74,\n        \"rxn_005\": 0.22,\n        \"rxn_007\": 0.08,\n        \"rxn_008\": 0.9,\n        \"rxn_010\": 0.42,\n        \"rxn_011\": 0.38,\n        \"rxn_012\": 0.14,\n        \"rxn_013\": 0.52\n      },\n      \"chemical_feasibility\": 0.47,\n      \"pathway_coherence\": 0.66,\n      \"environmental_progression\": 0.79,\n      \"target_achievement\": 0.58,\n      \"overall_confidence\": 0.57,\n      \"feedback\": \"The early hydrothermal